<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Nova Confirmação de Compra</title>
  </head>
  <body style="margin: 0; padding: 0; background-color: #f2f2f0; font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif; color: #1f2a44;">
    <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="background-color: #f2f2f0; padding: 28px 12px;">
      <tr>
        <td align="center">
          <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="max-width: 620px; background-color: #ffffff; border-radius: 22px; overflow: hidden; border: 1px solid #e1e4ea; box-shadow: 0 8px 28px rgba(31, 42, 68, 0.09);">
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 28px 30px 20px 30px; background: linear-gradient(165deg, #f7f8f9 0%, #eef1f4 56%, #f8f8f8 100%);">
                <div style="font-size: 12px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: #7c8598; margin-bottom: 12px;">Nova Confirmação</div>
                <h1 style="margin: 0; font-size: 30px; line-height: 1.2; color: #17223b; font-weight: 700;">
                  Um novo presente foi confirmado
                </h1>
                <p style="margin: 14px 0 0 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.55; color: #3a4255;">
                  Evento: <strong>{{ eventName }}</strong>
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 0 30px 0 30px;">
                <table role="presentation" width="100%" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0; margin-top: 10px; background-color: #f9fbfe; border: 1px solid #dbe2ec; border-radius: 16px; overflow: hidden;">
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 18px 18px 8px 18px; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #7f899e;">Convidado</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0 18px 16px 18px; font-size: 17px; line-height: 1.4; color: #1f2a44; font-weight: 600;">
                      {{ guestName }}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0 18px 16px 18px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.5; color: #5f687c; border-top: 1px solid #e5e9f0;">
                      {{ guestEmail }}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0 18px 8px 18px; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #7f899e; border-top: 1px solid #e5e9f0;">Produto</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0 18px 16px 18px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #1f2a44;">
                      {{ giftName }}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0 18px 8px 18px; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #7f899e; border-top: 1px solid #e5e9f0;">Quantidade</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0 18px 16px 18px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5; color: #1f2a44;">
                      {{ quantity }}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0 18px 8px 18px; font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1px; color: #7f899e; border-top: 1px solid #e5e9f0;">Mensagem de carinho</td>
                  </tr>
                  <tr>
                    <td style="padding: 0 18px 20px 18px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.6; color: #1f2a44;">
                      {{ notes ?? 'Nao informada' }}
                    </td>
                  </tr>
                </table>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 18px 30px 28px 30px;">
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.6; color: #5f687c;">
                  A confirmacao foi registrada no painel administrativo e o contador do presente ja foi atualizado.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 14px 30px 16px 30px; background-color: #f7f8fa; border-top: 1px solid #e6e9ef;">
                <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 12px; line-height: 1.5; color: #8a92a3;">
                  Este e-mail foi enviado automaticamente pelo Baby Shower API.
                </p>
              </td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table>
  </body>
</html>
